        "captions": "[{\"start\": 0, \"end\": 9072000, \"text\": \"国外玩突然不舒服怎么说？\\n收藏这 5 句，覆盖说症状、要药品、问路、求助送医等不同需求\\n1. I feel sick to my stomach.\\n2. Do you have stomach medicine?\\n3. Can I have some hot water?\\n4. Where is the nearest pharmacy?\\n5. Please call an ambulance.\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 9072000, \"end\": 13512000, \"text\": \"I feel sick to my stomach.\\n我胃不舒服\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 13512000, \"end\": 17952000, \"text\": \"Do you have stomach medicine?\\n你有胃药吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 17952000, \"end\": 22776000, \"text\": \"Can I have some hot water?\\n能给我一点热水吗？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 22776000, \"end\": 28440000, \"text\": \"Where is the nearest pharmacy?\\n最近的药店在哪里？\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 28440000, \"end\": 33912000, \"text\": \"Please call an ambulance.\\n请帮我叫救护车\", \"font_size\": 10}, {\"start\": 33912000, \"end\": 37536000, \"text\": \"你们出去玩有没有过突然不舒服的经历呀？\", \"font_size\": 10}]",
